Walled City Park. I don&amp;rsquo;t really remember much about my intentions behind the
photo beyond &lt;em&gt;this looks cool&lt;/em&gt;, although that is how I shoot most of the time.
In hindsight, I would&amp;rsquo;ve liked to have framed slightly to the right to show a
bit more of the truck and a bit less of the side of the building but I think
overall the framing is quite interesting. The depth of field puts a slight
softness on the shop fronts which I think works well to make the two guys on the
trucks stand out a bit as well as giving the road, and that piece of litter, a
more noticeable softness in the foreground. The one guy on the right stands out
really well, framed perfectly in front of the white board, but I think the other
guy, especially his head, blends into the background a bit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I don&amp;rsquo;t actually know if they are scrap collectors, but that&amp;rsquo;s what it looks
like to me.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Macaque</title><link>https://samsm.ch/photo/9204/</link><pubDate>Wed, 20 Jun 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://samsm.ch/photo/9204/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Cavern Cascade</title><link>https://samsm.ch/photo/8505/</link><pubDate>Sat, 05 May 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://samsm.ch/photo/8505/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Subways 01</title><link>https://samsm.ch/photo/8405/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 May 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://samsm.ch/photo/8405/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Two Leaves</title><link>https://samsm.ch/photo/8101/</link><pubDate>Thu, 12 Apr 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://samsm.ch/photo/8101/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Barranco de los Mocanes</title><link>https://samsm.ch/photo/7512/</link><pubDate>Tue, 13 Mar 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://samsm.ch/photo/7512/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Clifton Bridge</title><link>https://samsm.ch/photo/7102/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://samsm.ch/photo/7102/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>